LIBRAWDIST
==========

librawdist - A secure, modular package manager library for the Rawssg
ecosystem. Create, fetch, verify, install, and remove `.rawdist` archives
with SHA‑256 integrity checks, atomic manifest handling, and a high‑level
`PackageManager` facade.

Version  : 0.5.0
License  : GPL-3.0
Website  : https://github.com/mroczect/librawdist
Rust     : Edition 2024


